CKPool [[mining pool|Pooled_mining]].

CKPool was started on the 20th of September, 2014  (1.1)

The pool and pool software is created and run by the [[CGMiner]] developers


## Servers to use

* Stratum - Use for ALL stratum capable Bitcoin mining software
	stratum+tcp://stratum.kano.is:3333 USA

##Reward distribution

* Pay Per Last N Shares PPLNS - see: [[Comparison_of_mining_pools]]
* 0.9% fee
* Pay out TXN fees
* Payout after 120 confirmations.

##Extra features

* Email notification of change to account settings
* Email on payout
* IRC chanel at irc.freenode.net #ckpool
* API in json

##How to run miners

**CGMiner [Forum](https://bitcointalk.org/index.php?topic=28402.0)**<br />

cgminer.exe -o stratum+tcp://stratum.kano.is:3333 -u username_workername -p X

